StZDCUtil package

-----------------------------------------------
1. StZDCDb

The database interface.
Provides access to the following DB tables:
zdcsmdPed
zdcsmdGain
zdcsmdBeamCenter
zdcCalib
This class can read and write text files, 
access DB via St_db_Maker or directly via StDbManager.

macros/test_db
Automatic testing macro "test_db". 
Run it without arguments and look for "All tests PASSED" in the output.

-----------------------------------------------
2. StZDCGeom

The description of ZDC geometry in the STAR coordinate system.

-----------------------------------------------
3. StZDCUtil

Miscellaneous utility functions.

-----------------------------------------------
